categories: Category:Imperial Navy personnel of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Yago was a male veteran of the Imperial Starfleet. In 34 ABY, he was an officer holding the rank of captain in the First Order on board Supreme Leader Snoke's Mega-class Star Dreadnought, the Supremacy. The starship had been under the command of Yago prior to General Armitage Hux's transferral from the Finalizer.
